{"tid":918256,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈5人師弟團確定出道！BIGHIT證實了","createTime":"2018-11-27T05:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:01:46.000Z","uid":188406,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e6f2c118709ddac980070c16b211a3839c27dc","tid":918256,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"南韓夯團防彈少年團（BTS）在全球都有高人氣和關注度，所屬的BigHit娛樂也成為2017年最賺錢的經紀公司，不過BTS是目前公司旗下唯一一組團體，不斷有消息傳出他們的「師弟團」將出道，終於27日BigHit證實，5人新男團預計將於2019年年初出道。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，BigHit娛樂確定將在2019年年初推出5人男團，這是繼防彈少年團之後，睽違6年推出的新團，雖然新人團的團名、走向風格等細節都還未公開，但光是被冠上「防彈少年的弟弟團」，就讓業界抱持高度期待。對此，BigHit也坦承確有此事，但詳細事項還沒完全確定。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，CJ E&amp;M今年8月也證實將和BIGHIT娛樂合作建立新公司，有計畫建立一個新的經紀公司Belief，並在韓國、美國、中國、日本等地進行海選，以全球為範圍推出選秀節目，希望培養出下一代「引領韓流的全球化偶像組合」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1316763?from=fb_et_korea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1316763%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_korea&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=cb6be140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1316763?from=fb_et_korea</a><br />\n又一天團準備堀起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca96a32d720cbe2b1ffadd3789929369dd3b4499","tid":918256,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"唔知BTS班師弟姣唔姣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bfffbffc5086059dddaed70e3d0a3747bc1616","tid":918256,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"個名都柒過人<br />\n乜撚野防彈少年團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去打北韓啦仆街"},{"pid":"ac59ef4f9c9f5ff0c6aa7f839991e1106483e9a2","tid":918256,"uid":10652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82bfffbffc5086059dddaed70e3d0a3747bc1616","tid":91